Platform SDK Java 9.0 API Reference
  • All Classes
 

Package com.genesyslab.platform.apptemplate.filtering.impl.configuration

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CustomTypeSupport
    Custom filter should implement this interface.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConditionParser
    Creates condition ContainsAny with message attribute AttributeOperand or MessageTypeOperand and constant value ConstantOperand.
    ConstantValueParser
    Parses filter option and creates list of constant values ValueList that can be used in filter conditions FilterCondition or filter actions FilterAction.
    For example:
    DefaultFilterFactory
    Factory for the FilterGroup objects.
    FilterChainConfiguration
    This class keeps filter chain FilterChain and it's settings that can be modified at runtime.
    FilterChainFactory
    This class is used internally by the FilterConfigurationHelper to create or upgrade filter configuration.
    FilterChainFactory.EntryConfiguration
    Represents entry from the list of filters, assigned to the protocol in the "Connection" tab of application configuration window.
    FilterChainNotificationHandler
    Implements MessageFilter to decide whether message should be logged or not upon internal message filter chain.
    FilterConfigurationParser
    Base class for the filter option parsers.
    FilterFactory
    Creates or modifies filter regarding provided configuration options.
